$Id$

Contains support scripts that gets installed under '${sysconfdir}/tvpvrd/'

Files:

tvpvrd.conf                 Main configuration script for the daemon

tvpvrd.css                  CSS Stylesheet for WEB-interface
tvpvrd_mobile.css           CSS Stylesheet for WEB-interface for mobile phone browser

postrec_processing.sh       Script that will be called after each recording has finished
shutdown.sh                 Script that will be called to do automatic server shutdown
switchchannel.sh            Script that can be used to do external channel switching


